## Files

- `dashboard.html` - Main dashboard showing current sprint metrics
- `historical_dashboard.html` - 12-month historical trends analysis
- `update_dashboard_template.py` - Template for automation script (add your credentials)
- `update_dashboard.py` - Local script with credentials (gitignored for security)

## Setup

1. Copy `update_dashboard_template.py` to `update_dashboard.py`
2. Add your Jira credentials to `update_dashboard.py`
3. Run the script to update both dashboards# rse-volatility-dashboard
RSE Team Jira Backlog Volatility Dashboard - Real-time metrics 
